{"tid":2144821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【急】被外國制裁算唔算干犯公職人員行為失當罪？","createTime":"2020-08-07T18:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T18:24:23.000Z","uid":311358,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2547b996e14a24a9b279484c6630637295a854b0","tid":2144821,"uid":311358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T18:23:24.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n<br />\n有關的失當行為必須是故意作出而並非無心之失，也就是說，有關公職人員是知道他的行為違法，或是故意罔顧他的行為有違法之嫌，卻無合理辯解或理由，因此須負上刑責。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hksargegu.org.hk/public_html/S%20Topic/CS%20BOOKLET/MIPO_Booklet_TC_2012.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhksargegu.org.hk%2Fpublic_html%2FS%2520Topic%2FCS%2520BOOKLET%2FMIPO_Booklet_TC_2012.pdf&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6IleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=cee1af77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hksargegu.org.hk/public_html/S%20Topic/CS%20BOOKLET/MIPO_Booklet_TC_2012.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"93da6da02c3bf0ff4314227d080c976d2f30c87c","tid":2144821,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T18:24:23.000Z","msg":"應該掉返轉黎問<br />\n如果無被外國制裁係咪代表唔夠愛國，係咪違反就職時宣誓誓言？"}]}